      <h1>Bachelors</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        Are you looking for a bachelor’s programme at a world-class Dutch university? Leiden University offers upwards of 50 bachelor’s programmes, 12 of which are taught in English: you’re certain to find one that suits you.</p>
      </article>
